				<div class="row equalize">
					<div class="col-xs-6 col-md-3" id="dan-jackson">
						<div class="image"><img src="images/speakers/dan-jackson.png"></div>
						<p class="margin-bottom-10">Dan Jackson<br><span class="small">Executive Director, NuLawLab, Northeastern University School of Law</span></p>
                                                <div class="margin-bottom-30">
                                                        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/dan-jackson-66898513/" class="icon linkedin margin-right-5" target="_blank">LinkedIn</a>
